===Transitive verb===
'''feng shui''' (''third-person singular present tense'' '''[[feng shuis]]''', ''simple past and past participle'' '''[[feng shuied]]''', ''present participle'' '''[[feng shuiing]]''')

# To arrange a space according to the rules of feng shui.
#: ''I'm going to have my bedroom '''feng shuied'''. Maybe this will finally bring me good luck.''

